The three suspects in the farm attack at Marchlands in which Sue Howarth was killed, have appeared before the Belfast Magistrate&#8217;s Court where bail was denied on Monday morning.They have been identified as Themba William Yika, Nkosinathi Yika and Lucas Makua. All three were out on bail on another case relating to stock theft on the Bergendal Farm last year.The accused were allegedly found in possession of a camera, cellphones and bank card belonging to the deceased.&nbsp;&nbsp;